      "rationale": "Three-level mesh refinement study performed on the pedicle screw shank and rod-screw interface regions. Stiffness QoI changed by 1.4% between medium (element edge ~0.3 mm) and fine (edge ~0.15 mm) meshes. Richardson extrapolation GCI < 0.8%. Final mesh uses medium density for computational efficiency with demonstrated convergence."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorType": "Numerical solver error",
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "requiredLevel": 2,
